    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Great Good-Condition Find \u2013 Dependable, Well-Kept & Ready to Roll! \ud83d\ude97\n\nHere's a wonderful chance to get into a genuinely well-maintained vehicle that's been looked after! We'll be straight with you: this car shows normal wear consistent with its age, but it runs well, presents nicely, and has plenty of life left in it. No hidden surprises here \u2014 just a solid, reliable ride at a fair and honest price. If you're looking for dependable daily transportation with good overall condition, this one is absolutely worth a look!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good condition, and we're committed to giving you a fully transparent picture of what you're purchasing. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains a solid shine with only minor surface wear consistent with regular use, and while you may notice the occasional small scratch or light scuff upon close inspection, there are no significant dents or structural concerns. The interior is clean and comfortable, with upholstery that shows normal signs of use but no major tears, stains, or damage. Mechanically, this car has been maintained and runs reliably \u2014 the engine starts smoothly, the transmission shifts without issue, and the brakes respond well. All major systems are in working order, and this vehicle is ready for everyday driving without the need for immediate repairs. This is a solid, dependable car at a fair price for its condition \u2014 a great option for a buyer looking for reliable transportation without paying mint-condition prices.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition, and we want to be fully transparent so you can make an informed decision. The exterior is in rough shape \u2014 expect significant rust on the body panels, deep scratches, and paint that has faded and peeled in multiple areas. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery, cracked dashboard components, and general deterioration throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the vehicle has known issues that will require attention \u2014 it starts and moves, but should not be considered reliable transportation without substantial repair work. This listing is best suited for a buyer looking for a project vehicle, a parts source, or someone with the skills and budget to invest in a full restoration. We are pricing it accordingly and honestly at $5,500 to reflect its current state.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a fair-condition car, suitable for buyers seeking affordable, functional transportation who are comfortable with a vehicle that shows its age. The exterior displays several visible signs of wear, including surface scratches, minor dents, and some paint fading \u2014 nothing that compromises structural integrity, but enough to be noticeable at a glance. The interior is functional with expected wear on seating surfaces, trim pieces, and controls; it's clean but clearly used. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though buyers should anticipate that some components may be approaching the end of their service life and could require attention in the near to medium term. This is an honest, no-frills listing for a car that will get you where you need to go without the premium price tag of a higher-condition vehicle.",
      "price": 17000.0,
